title: Michel Petrucciani (Michael Radford, 2011)
description:
Synopsis:

Suffering from brittle-bone disease, Michel Petrucciani overcame his handicap to become an internationally renowned artist. Michael Radford retraces the portrait of this great jazz pianist. What are the sources of his sublime inspiration and how are they expressed?


Directed: Michael Radford.
France, 2011.
